![colordistance](../images/science/colordistance2019.jpg)

A methods paper for my R package, `colordistance`, which allows users to compare the color palette similarities of images in a variety of ways. The project itself lives [here](https://github.com/hiweller/colordistance/) and the documentation lives [here](https://hiweller.github.io/colordistance/).

[Download](http://hiweller.github.io/files/Weller2019_colordistance.pdf)
